	   <tr><td colspan=2>You're screenshots that you've taken in the game will be by default in C:\Program Files\Everquest folder.  They are the only *.bmp files in the folder but they are named with numbers.  So, just right-click and choose sort by type and find the bitmaps.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
