	   <tr><td colspan=2>South Karana is an awesome place. You can hunt treants, higher level aviaks, and gnolls. You can also get a group and go into Splitpaw. In Kunark the Frontier Mountains are a good spot for grouping at your level. In east karana, there is a druid ring. Get two other casters that are about your level, and you will be able to take it. Also, in the ocean of tears there are dwarfs and sisters on the sister island that are great exp.<br><br>Former Addict of Everquest.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
