	   <tr><td colspan=2>As Nunnin states, considering your pet will give you approximate level. Go to www.magecompendium.com for more info on all Mage related stuff. To answer the question, if you're 16, let's say, and you conjure a 17th level pet, it will hit an 18th level MoB pretty well. The problem will be your spells being resisted. Only chase after certain red /cons in group or until you get Malise at 24. One thing of note - DO NOT kill your pet if you conjure and it /cons blue. I see too many posts where this advice is given. Throw that pet into a fight and see how it does. If it dies, oh well. If it lives, there's one more mob for the price of your summon gem.<br>&nbsp;<br>Aaneldarie Tura'Seorsa<br>29th Season Magician  Vazaelle</td></tr>
