	   <tr><td colspan=2>You need to target your pet and do a "con" on it, thats the only real way to see what its aprox level is. When you cast a pet it depends on the spell level of the pet, AND the level of your mage as to if it cons blue, yellow, etc. <br><br>I just started my mage and can cast a pet that cons blue, kill it and cast again and get yellow, so there is only a little bit of flux in there. As I go up in level I have seen my pets con more blue than yellow untill I get my next spells.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
